If you are a windows 10 user and you face problem on downloading packages then this might help:
After installing Atom check in packages if it is searching packages name or not ,if not then follow below steps:
 File--Exit
 start atom again and search packages which you want to install
 For eg-"emmet" is the package you want search 
 File--settings--install --type"emmet" --install
 The end.
